{"tid":188912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(有片)【中國製造】名創優品被外界轟山寨 反指被抄襲","createTime":"2017-04-06T04:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T05:06:56.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52e3f686571febcac71e30501391ddc4da777373","tid":188912,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170406/large/06ls2p02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170406%2Flarge%2F06ls2p02.jpg&h=fc34c717&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近年大舉進軍本港的內地雜貨店名創優品（Miniso），其香港、澳門及台灣區域總經理衛肇泉表示，2015年香港分店只有23間，去年底已達50間，發展迅速，今年以雙位數增長為擴張目標，商場、港鐵站均會考慮。他指，本港產品價格最多為20至40元，而每單平均消費約44元，即通常買2件貨品。MINISO一直被指為日本品牌的「山寨版」，衛肇泉反而指，現時有其他店舖疑似抄襲MINISO，更在MINISO分店旁邊開店，舖內設計均十分相似。<br />\n<br />\nMINISO以快速雜貨形式營運，他指香港貨品種類3,000款，不斷以新產品淘汰現有貨品。MINISO共同創辦人兼日本首席設計師三宅順也指，設計團隊有30-40人，大部分產品均會親自過目，很高興是次有機會與香港、挪威設計師合作。<br />\n<br />\nMINISO全球店數超過2,000間，未來將進軍北歐，拓展分店至挪威，由挪威、香港混血兒Chun Wai Tsui（徐俊威）以加盟商形式營運。他表示，對比北歐其他平價生活品牌，MINISO定位更高、質量亦有保證。<br />\n<br />\n名創優品自2014年進軍本港，以10元價格出售日式產品，於去年又被指抄襲本地插畫師江記及Darylhochi作品製成精品出售，名創優品官網聲稱創辦人「三宅順也」是多個國際休閒時尚品牌設計師，但有報道指網上及過去的報道均未能找到此人資料。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170405&amp;guid=56524575&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170405%26guid%3D56524575%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&d=1mfmSgVVN%2FWy7xf%2FaESqF%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=80a011ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170405%26guid%3D56524575%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&h=52ce2d62\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170405&amp;guid=56524575&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"8fbf4ec36794c4729aba784eb51f97b761419776","tid":188912,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:02:31.000Z","msg":"個大陸佬又幾眉清目秀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4109cbd9f5170f4f91eabdcc400294bc8eab673d","tid":188912,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:26:09.000Z","msg":"同啲用蝗語又唔認嘅人一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9091f6d93ee11c036ec504acde78e0a9fb781a4e","tid":188912,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:00:00.000Z","msg":"淘寶貨色<br />\n永不幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d76ea304baca40ba28c2da36427cb3a7a229b1","tid":188912,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:06:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">MINISO一直被指為日本品牌的「山寨版」，衛肇泉反而指，現時有其他店舖疑似抄襲MINISO，更在MINISO分店旁邊開店，舖內設計均十分相似。</span><br />\n<br />\n語言偽術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c4f03c940ea92ed304fa07431bc2e435b5697e","tid":188912,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"296d3ed7837843d69f5f7fd3252cef2cbdd5c030","tid":188912,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:49:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個大陸佬又幾眉清目秀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪扮緊木村"},{"pid":"b71e278b74869dc410fd2b9e013fad0fd8b06bf4","tid":188912,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c7c9f1f224afe089b6b7f9b1ed7eaba71b5b6e","tid":188912,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:08:27.000Z","msg":"無印u記擺明抄佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.g